inactivity_minutes: 30

turns_since_last: 3
 
pause_topic_turns: 8

suggestion_life_hours: 24

**Explanations:**
*   `history_message_count`: Number of messages from the conversation history
    injected into the suggestions generation prompt.
*   `inactivity_minutes`: Number of minutes since the last message to trigger
    suggestions generation.
*   `turns_since_last`: Number of conversation turns since the last selected
    suggestion to trigger suggestions generation.
*   `pause_topic_turns`: Number of conversation turns to stop changing the topic
    when a suggestion topic is selected.
*   `suggestion_life_hours`: Number of hours the suggestions will live in
    memory.